languages.text: "Я никогда не говорил, что исполнить этот план просто. Путь к лаборатории и комнате охраны перекрыт безумцами, что захватили станцию. Они не идут на переговоры, их не пугает гнев Императора и Навис Нобилите. Только грубая сила — коей в моем распоряжении не так уж и много".

languages.text: "I never said the feat would be easy to accomplish. The path to the laboratory and the guard room is blocked by the very same madmen who took over the station. They will not negotiate and are not afraid of displeasing the Navis Nobilite or incurring the Emperor's wrath. They bow only to brute strength, something which I currently happen to lack."

languages.text: «No he dicho que fuera fácil. Los lunáticos que han tomado la estación también han bloqueado el camino que lleva al laboratorio y a la sala de guardia. No están dispuestos a negociar y no temen contrariar a la Navis Nobilite ni provocar la ira del Emperador. Solo es posible someterlos a fuerza bruta, algo de lo que no dispongo en estos momentos».

languages.text: "Ich habe nie gesagt, dass es leicht zu bewerkstelligen sein würde. Der Weg zum Laboratorium und zum Wachraum wird von denselben Wahnsinnigen blockiert, die die Station in ihre Gewalt gebracht haben. Sie werden nicht verhandeln, und sie haben keine Angst davor, die Navis Nobilite zu verärgern oder den Zorn des Imperators auf sich zu ziehen. Sie gehen nur vor roher Stärke in die Knie, die mir im Moment leider fehlt."

languages.text: « Je n'ai jamais dit que l'exploit serait facile à accomplir. L'accès au laboratoire et à la salle des gardes est bloqué par les mêmes déments qui ont pris le contrôle de la station. Ils refuseront tout dialogue et n'ont pas peur de se mettre la Navis Nobilite à dos ou de provoquer la colère de l'Empereur. Ils ne s'inclinent que face à la force brute, ce qui me fait passablement défaut pour le moment. »
languages.original_text: "I never said the feat would be easy to accomplish. The path to the laboratory and the guard room is blocked by the very same madmen who took over the station. languages.text: “我从来没说过这是件简单的事情。这座星站上到处都是疯子，通往实验室与警卫室的道路都被那些疯子堵住了。他们根本无法说服，也根本不怕惹恼导航宗族或激起帝皇的怒火，只有蛮力能让他们让路，而这正是我目前欠缺的东西。”
languages.original_text: "I never said the feat would be easy to accomplish. The path to the laboratory and the guard room is blocked by the very same madmen who took over the station. They will not negotiate and are not afraid of displeasing the Navis Nobilite or incurring the Emperor's wrath. They bow only to brute strength, something which I currently happen to lack."

languages.text: 「この一大事を簡単に収められるとは一言も言っていない。研究室と警備室への道は、まさにこのステーションを乗っ取ったイカれた奴らが塞いでいる。奴らは交渉を受け入れず、航宙貴族の怒りを買うことも、皇帝の怒りを受けることも恐れてはいない。非人道的な力で押さえつけるしかないが、今の私には間が悪いことに、その力が足りない」
languages.original_text: "I never said the feat would be easy to accomplish. The path to the laboratory and the guard room is blocked by the very same madmen who took over the station. They will not negotiate and are not afraid of displeasing the Navis Nobilite or incurring the Emperor's wrath. They bow only to brute strength, something which I currently happen to lack."

languages.text: "Ağzımdan, kolay diye bir söz çıkmadı. O dediğim manyaklar, laboratuvara ve muhafız koğuşuna giden yolları kapadı. Bunlar lafla yola gelmez. Navis Nobilite'nin şerrinden, İmparator'un gazabından çekinmez. Anca kaba kuvvetten anlarlar ki o da bende tükenmiş vaziyette."
